.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_paint_colour -  This method adds a paint colour to the shop and how much that  colour costs to use.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_paint_colour(string colour,
int cost)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^colour%^RESET%^ - the colour of the paint
%^BOLD%^cost%^RESET%^ - the cost of the paint

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/sign_writer.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a paint colour to the shop and how much that 
colour costs to use.  The cost for the colour is the cost per
letter.
.EP

